description: Runes derive from sounds believed to be associated with power. These sounds were encoded as symbols and they too appeared to tap into something powerful. The symbols appear carved on graves and in rock.  Runes can be invoked to answer questions, and assist in decision making.  This application lists the 24 runs of the Younger Futhark - the 24 runes of power. Maybe. What's to lose.
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask Nordic Runes for a rune
Alexa  ask Nordic Runes about runes
Alexa ask Nordic Runes to say a Nordic Rune
name: Nordic Runes
